Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.60,0:00:06.23,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,見つけたぞ　人虎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.71,0:00:06.23,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,I've found you, weretiger.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.72,0:00:11.06,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,Akutagawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.83,0:00:10.19,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,芥川
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.31,0:00:22.57,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,Looks like you've improved your \Nacrobatic skills, weretiger.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.39,0:00:22.58,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,曲芸の腕は上げたようだな　人虎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.57,0:00:25.08,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,Why are you here, Akutagawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.87,0:00:25.08,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,何をしに来た　芥川
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.91,0:00:27.84,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,貴様を殺しに
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:27.83,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,To kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.41,0:00:31.08,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,Don't you understand the \Nsituation we're in right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.44,0:00:31.13,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,今がどんな時かわかっている筈だ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.45,0:00:34.37,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,僕達の居場所がなくなるかもしれないんだぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.49,0:00:34.30,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,We may no longer have a place to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.08,0:00:38.10,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,僕にはお前が微塵も理解できない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.17,0:00:38.09,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,I don't understand you one bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.31,0:00:40.80,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,I don't remember ever asking \Nfor your understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.38,0:00:40.81,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,理解を求めた覚えはない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.19,0:00:42.72,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,やれやれ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.23,0:00:42.74,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,Oh, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.72,0:00:46.94,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,芥川君の独走癖は相変わらずだなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.77,0:00:47.01,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,Akutagawa-kun still has a \Nterrible habit of going solo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.02,0:00:49.25,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,仕方ない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.15,0:00:49.28,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.79,0:00:50.78,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,敦君
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.79,0:00:53.39,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,Atsushi-kun, we don't have \Ntime to deal with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.02,0:00:54.90,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,彼に係っている暇はない　先に進もう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.39,0:00:54.90,Stray Dogs - Italics,Dazai,0,0,0,,Let's move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.90,0:00:55.98,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.90,0:00:55.99,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ですが…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.98,0:00:57.59,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.22,0:01:00.20,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,大丈夫　私の云う通りにすれば逃げられるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.59,0:01:00.18,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,Just do as I say, and you'll make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.01,0:01:04.32,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,わかりました
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.14,0:01:04.40,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.78,0:01:10.11,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,Akutagawa, I'm speaking to \NDazai-san on this intercom.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.84,0:01:06.96,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,芥川
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.05,0:01:10.12,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,このインカムは太宰さんと繋がってる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.54,0:01:13.15,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,He wants to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.57,0:01:12.94,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,話があるそうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.91,0:01:16.79,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,Dazai-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.94,0:01:16.44,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,太宰さん
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.02,0:01:27.15,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,太宰さん
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.11,0:01:27.13,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,Dazai-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.38,0:03:04.61,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,やあ　ゼルダ　元気にしてたか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.44,0:03:03.17,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,Well hello, Zelda.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.17,0:03:04.61,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,How have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.33,0:03:07.74,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,Yeah, I apologize for calling you so late.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.36,0:03:07.75,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,あぁ　電話が遅れたのは謝るよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.70,0:03:10.01,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,I heard the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.72,0:03:11.92,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,聞いたぞ　またシェフを解雇したのか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.01,0:03:11.94,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,You laid off another chef?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.92,0:03:15.28,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,せっかく欧州の最高級レストランから…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.53,0:03:15.75,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,They came all the way here from \Na top-notch European restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.19,0:03:20.39,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,いや　責めてなんかいないさ　本当だ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.34,0:03:19.32,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,No, I don't blame you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.32,0:03:20.38,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.79,0:03:24.01,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,君のクリームチーズ嫌いを知らない料理人なんて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.82,0:03:26.48,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,Any cook that doesn't know of your distaste \Nfor cream cheese ought to perish.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.26,0:03:26.42,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,世界から滅びればいい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.90,0:03:31.36,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,そう　あの子はまだロンドンに留学中だ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.96,0:03:31.35,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,Yes, she's still studying in London.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.72,0:03:35.66,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,勿論あの子のことも一秒だって忘れやしないさ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.94,0:03:35.88,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,I wouldn't forget it for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.32,0:03:39.65,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,Sorry, it appears I have a guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.48,0:03:41.10,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,悪いが　客人のようだ　また電話する
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.65,0:03:41.05,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,I'll call you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.76,0:03:43.85,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,I love you, Zelda.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.82,0:03:43.87,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,愛してるよ　ゼルダ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.20,0:03:49.32,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,That was a brief farewell, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.45,0:03:49.33,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,短い別れだったな　少年
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.88,0:03:53.33,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,捜し物は　これか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.97,0:03:53.33,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,Is this what you're looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.72,0:03:56.43,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,貴方が制御端末を守るガード？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.78,0:03:56.79,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,Are you the one guarding \Nthe control terminal?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.79,0:04:01.49,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,Here's the first secret \Nto how I got this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.80,0:04:01.39,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,俺がここまで登り詰めた成功の秘訣その一だ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.26,0:04:07.57,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,仕事で一番大事な部分は他人任せにしない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.51,0:04:07.41,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,The most important part of any job is to \Nnot leave anything for others to handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.23,0:04:12.16,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ところで　この「白鯨」の重量を知っているか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.49,0:04:12.26,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,By the way, do you know how \Nmuch the Moby Dick weighs?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.01,0:04:15.38,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,総重量二万九千トン
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.04,0:04:15.70,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,It has a total mass of 29,000 tons.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.70,0:04:18.23,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,Dropped from an altitude of two kilometers,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.79,0:04:18.15,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,上空２キロから落すれば
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.15,0:04:21.97,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,TNT爆弾百四十トン相当のエネルギーが
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.23,0:04:25.80,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,it would explode with the force of 140 tons of TNT... \NRight in the middle of the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.66,0:04:25.77,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,市内のど真ん中で炸裂する
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.47,0:04:29.96,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな非道…絶対に許されない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.57,0:04:30.28,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,No one would allow such an atrocity.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.28,0:04:34.97,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,The second secret to how I got this far is: \Ndon't let the values of others affect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.32,0:04:32.12,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,秘訣その二
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.12,0:04:35.00,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,他人の価値観に流されるな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.89,0:04:38.81,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,とはいえ　君も俺も忙しい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.94,0:04:39.21,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,With that said, you and I are both busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.50,0:04:43.46,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,If we have to fight over the control \Nterminal, let's keep things simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.54,0:04:43.52,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,その制御端末を奪い合うなら　簡潔に行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.15,0:04:49.32,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,三つ数えたら同時に走り　先に端末を手にしたほうが勝者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.20,0:04:46.55,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,We'll both run towards it \Non the count of three.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.55,0:04:49.58,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,The first of us to take it is the winner.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.58,0:04:52.99,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,If you win, you can do as you like\N with the Moby Dick.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.67,0:04:52.98,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,君が勝てば　「白鯨」は好きに動かせ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.79,0:05:00.11,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,だが俺が勝てば　君は俺に服従し　捜し物を手伝ってもらう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.89,0:05:00.11,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,But if I win, you'll serve me \Nin helping with my search.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.69,0:05:01.82,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ワン
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.73,0:05:01.80,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,One...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.21,0:05:05.53,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,勝負に乗って　合図と同時に走るか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.25,0:05:05.53,Stray Dogs - Italics,Atsushi,0,0,0,,Should I take his challenge \Nand run when he does?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.11,0:05:06.98,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,Two...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.11,0:05:06.99,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ツー
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.98,0:05:10.99,Stray Dogs - Italics,Atsushi,0,0,0,,No, I can't trust anyone from \Nthe Guild to keep a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.99,0:05:10.42,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,いや　ギルドの口約束なんて信用できない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.92,0:05:13.00,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,裏をかいて合図より前に奪い
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.99,0:05:14.74,Stray Dogs - Italics,Atsushi,0,0,0,,I'll outsmart him and take it \Nbefore his signal, and run!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.00,0:05:14.54,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,そのまま逃げる
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.25,0:05:17.55,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,スリー
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.32,0:05:17.62,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.89,0:05:21.61,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,秘訣その三
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.94,0:05:27.09,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,Secret number three: It's easy to predict the \Nbehavior of anyone who's given an opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.97,0:05:27.02,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,好機を与えられた人間の行動は読みやすい
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.79,0:05:32.30,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,Oh? You aren't going down with that kick?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.32,0:05:33.88,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,今の蹴りで倒れんか　大したものだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.30,0:05:34.30,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,That's impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.30,0:05:35.56,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.31,0:05:37.74,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,いいだろう　一万では失礼だったな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.56,0:05:38.05,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,10,000 may have been insulting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.54,0:05:42.28,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,This is a portion of my securities.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.58,0:05:42.32,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,これは俺が所有する有価証券の一部だ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.28,0:05:43.70,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,There's 100,000 dollars worth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.32,0:05:43.69,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,十万ドルある
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.08,0:05:47.36,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,I haven't introduced you \Nto my ability yet, have I?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.18,0:05:47.45,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,俺の異能力　紹介がまだだったな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.07,0:05:52.33,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,Ability: The Great Fitzgerald.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.28,0:05:52.33,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,異能力　「華麗なるフィッツジェラルド」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.72,0:06:03.71,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,俺の異能力は
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.90,0:06:09.47,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,My ability grants me physical \Nstrength equal to the money I spend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.34,0:06:09.76,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,消費した金額に比例して　身体能力を強化させる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.30,0:06:15.43,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,Be proud, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.31,0:06:15.45,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,誇っていいぞ　少年
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.43,0:06:18.19,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,I haven't used 100,000 \Ndollars in a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.45,0:06:17.88,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,十万も使うのは久し振りだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.19,0:06:22.56,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,Of course, Zelda would spend \Nthat much in a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.22,0:06:22.46,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,もっともゼルダなら　ひと月で消し飛ばす額だがな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.84,0:06:25.25,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,これで凡て予定通りだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.02,0:06:25.21,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,Now everything is going according to plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.21,0:06:28.84,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,With crashing the Moby Dick, \Nand with capturing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.25,0:06:28.95,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,「白鯨」の落下も　君の捕獲もな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.57,0:06:31.62,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ぼ…僕も…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.66,0:06:31.61,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.92,0:06:33.87,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,うちの作戦参謀は
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.96,0:06:35.71,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,Our strategist has the \Nability to make
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.16,0:06:38.92,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,手持ちの情報から未来を限定予言できる異能力者だからな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.71,0:06:39.09,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,limited precognitions based \Non what information she has.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.03,0:06:45.02,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,Now that I have you, it would \Nbe a pain if you got away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.16,0:06:42.83,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,却説　捕らえたはいいが
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.83,0:06:45.00,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,また逃げられたら面倒だ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.00,0:06:48.07,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,念の為　手足を外しておくか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.02,0:06:48.06,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,I should probably remove your \Narms and legs for good measure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.22,0:06:57.85,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,おや　珍しい客人だ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.24,0:06:57.84,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,Oh my, what an unusual guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.28,0:06:59.89,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,Mister...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.37,0:07:01.28,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ミスターアグラ…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.89,0:07:01.35,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,Agua?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.79,0:07:03.63,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,Aguagar?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.81,0:07:03.65,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,アーグラーか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.83,0:07:05.15,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,芥川
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.02,0:07:05.14,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,Akutagawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.10,0:07:08.75,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,That's the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.11,0:07:08.96,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,それだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.11,0:07:10.11,Stray Dogs Ep Title,Text,0,0,0,,Episode Twenty-Three\NRashoumon, The Tiger, \Nand The Last Emperor
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.33,0:07:19.90,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,Hey, Kyouka-chan, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.49,0:07:19.92,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,やあ　鏡花ちゃん　聞こえるかい
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.90,0:07:21.04,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,It's Dazai.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.92,0:07:21.04,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,太宰だ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.30,0:07:26.51,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,特務課と交渉してね　取り敢えず君を地上に降ろせることになった
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.39,0:07:23.36,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,We negotiated with the \NGifted Special Operations Division.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.36,0:07:26.50,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,We can bring you back down for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.83,0:07:29.54,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,その無人機の操縦方法を教えるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.85,0:07:29.50,Stray Dogs - Italics,Dazai,0,0,0,,I'm going to teach you \Nhow to pilot that drone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.03,0:07:32.54,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,もういい
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.20,0:07:32.41,Stray Dogs - Default,Kyouka,0,0,0,,No more.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.32,0:07:38.18,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,本当のことを云うとね
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.50,0:07:43.18,Stray Dogs - Italics,Dazai,0,0,0,,To tell you the truth, the Agency \Ndoesn't have a reason to rescue you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.68,0:07:42.72,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,探偵社には君を救助する理由がないのだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.60,0:07:47.31,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,You aren't an official member, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.65,0:07:47.22,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,何故なら君はまだ正式な社員ではないからだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.80,0:07:52.22,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,探偵社には入社試験があり　君はまだそれを通過していない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.84,0:07:52.27,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,The Agency has an entrance test, \Nand you haven't passed it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.69,0:07:54.11,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,探偵社員として
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.70,0:07:58.85,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,The test is to see if you have the heart and \Nstrength to help even complete strangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.11,0:07:58.81,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,見知らぬ人でも助ける心と強さを持っているか験す試験だ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.96,0:08:03.34,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,私はきっとその試験には…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.02,0:08:03.45,Stray Dogs - Italics,Kyouka,0,0,0,,I don't think I'd pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.47,0:08:08.00,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,気に入らないな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.54,0:08:07.89,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,I don't like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.80,0:08:13.49,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,A former killer isn't qualified \Nto become a good person.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.82,0:08:13.43,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,元殺し屋に善人になる資格はない
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.98,0:08:17.43,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,君は本気でそう思っているのか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.02,0:08:17.43,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,Do you truly believe that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.65,0:08:25.02,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,やぁ　ミスター芥川
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.67,0:08:27.15,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,Well, Mr. Akutagawa, I'd love to welcome \Nyou aboard, but as you can see, I'm busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.37,0:08:27.15,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,歓迎したいのは山々だが
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.65,0:08:30.92,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,誰の許可で床に転がってる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.76,0:08:31.08,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,Who gave you permission to lie around?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.52,0:08:33.12,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,今度は逃がさぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.52,0:08:33.15,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,You aren't getting away this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.12,0:08:34.78,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,立って戦え
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.15,0:08:34.78,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,Stand up and fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.49,0:08:37.49,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,最悪の状況だ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.53,0:08:37.48,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,Things couldn't get worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.42,0:08:40.82,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,矢っ張り僕には最初から…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.55,0:08:40.87,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,I was never ready to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.36,0:08:45.65,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,You said earlier that you \Ncouldn't understand me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.37,0:08:45.62,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,先刻貴様は　僕が理解できぬと云ったな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.07,0:08:49.71,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,僕からすれば　貴様こそ理解できぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.12,0:08:49.71,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,To me, you're completely incomprehensible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.92,0:08:54.84,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,その臆病な眼は　己の力も異能力も信じてない
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.06,0:08:54.84,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,Those fearful eyes have no faith in \Nyour own strength or gift,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.06,0:08:58.12,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,だのにいつも無謀な死闘に挑む
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.27,0:08:58.08,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,yet you always involve \Nyourself in futile battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.08,0:09:01.05,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,Where do you get that \Nincoherent self-respect?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.12,0:09:01.05,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,その矛盾した自尊はどこから来る
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.05,0:09:03.39,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,That's enough, little guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.05,0:09:03.43,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,その辺にしておけ　小男
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.39,0:09:06.61,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,I don't like being ignored.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.43,0:09:06.23,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,そうでなくても　俺は無視されるのが嫌い…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.34,0:09:08.43,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,黙れ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.36,0:09:08.42,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.42,0:09:10.51,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,My main course is the weretiger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.43,0:09:10.53,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,僕の主菜は人虎だ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.08,0:09:13.52,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,I'd like my dessert to sit quietly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.20,0:09:13.53,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,後菓子はそこで大人しくしていろ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.74,0:09:20.06,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,I hate being in second place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.91,0:09:20.08,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は二番手が嫌いでな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.06,0:09:22.69,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,I request our rankings be changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.31,0:09:23.21,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,序列の変更を要求する
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.78,0:09:25.38,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,いいだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.86,0:09:25.16,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.50,0:09:29.42,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,黒獣を素手で止めるだと
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.50,0:09:29.51,Stray Dogs - Italics,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,Did he stop Rashoumon with his bare hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.06,0:09:38.44,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,For your efforts, I'll teach you \Nthe fourth secret to success.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.15,0:09:38.38,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,頑張る君に成功の秘訣その四を教えてやる
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.78,0:09:39.85,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,要らぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.81,0:09:39.85,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,I don't need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.85,0:09:41.09,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,Rashoumon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.03,0:09:41.62,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,「羅生門」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.62,0:09:42.81,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,「黒波濤」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.65,0:09:42.82,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,Black Torrent!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.65,0:09:42.82,sign_16229_126_Black_Torrent_,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,Black Torrent
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.65,0:09:47.14,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,500,000 dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.78,0:09:47.35,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,五十万ドル
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.79,0:10:00.66,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,成功の秘訣その四だ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.89,0:10:05.76,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,The fourth secret to success: Though \Nthere are many forms of strength...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.78,0:10:03.62,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ただ強者たれ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.95,0:10:07.46,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,金と権力　異能力に地位
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.76,0:10:14.23,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,money and influence, gifts, social status... \N it helps to have all of them, the way I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.46,0:10:10.25,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,強さの種類は一つではないが
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.55,0:10:14.37,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,まぁ　俺のように凡てを持つのが無難だな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.51,0:10:16.65,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,虎がいない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.53,0:10:16.66,Stray Dogs - Italics,Francis,0,0,0,,The tiger's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.01,0:10:19.09,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,何が強者だ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.23,0:10:19.03,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,Strength my ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.03,0:10:23.30,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,Money and gifts don't \Nexist to blow up cities.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.09,0:10:23.72,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,金や異能力は地上の街を吹っ飛ばす為にあるんじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.30,0:10:28.18,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,Human strength exists to be shared with \Nthose who are in the depths of despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.72,0:10:28.19,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,人の強さは　悲しみの淵で藻掻く人に差し伸べる為にあるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.36,0:10:30.73,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,いかにもな誤解だな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.61,0:10:30.72,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,I'm not surprised that \Nyou'd make such a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.49,0:10:34.78,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,力は弱者を助ける為にあるのではない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.63,0:10:34.77,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,Strength doesn't exist to help the weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.77,0:10:39.57,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,The very essence of money-making \Nis to extract value from the weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.78,0:10:39.57,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,何故なら金儲けの本質は　弱者からの搾取だからだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.94,0:10:43.51,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,それで得た金を弱者を助ける為に使っても
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.96,0:10:43.48,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,To then offer that to the \Nweak is to repeat a pointless act,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.48,0:10:47.41,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,akin to swinging a door round and round.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.51,0:10:47.41,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ドアをスイングするのと同じ反復行為だ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.41,0:10:50.74,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,Strength must be used more meaningfully.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.41,0:10:50.74,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,力はもっと有意義なことに使わねばならん
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.65,0:10:56.75,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,その為に踏み潰される命は見ない振りか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.69,0:10:56.60,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,Do you pretend not to see the lives \Nthat are snubbed out to that end?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.60,0:10:59.09,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,By the snubbed out lives of the weak...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.75,0:10:59.09,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,踏み潰される弱者というのは
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.81,0:11:02.22,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,例えば昔の君のような？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.86,0:11:02.17,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,Do you mean, for example, your past self?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.98,0:11:06.85,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,君の過去は調べた
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.00,0:11:06.85,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,I looked up your history.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.32,0:11:12.93,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,君は幼少時代に二度殺されかけているね　孤児院の院長に
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.47,0:11:10.92,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,You were nearly killed, twice, \Nin your early childhood
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.92,0:11:13.43,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,by the president of your orphanage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.47,0:11:19.61,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,彼に蹴られて肋骨を折られた時　院長は云ったそうだな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.49,0:11:19.61,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,When he kicked you and broke \Nyour ribs, he said to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.61,0:11:24.07,Stray Dogs - Flashback,President,0,0,0,,Compared to what your parents \Ndid to you in your infancy,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.86,0:11:24.08,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,実の両親が赤子の貴様にしたことに比べれば
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.07,0:11:27.54,Stray Dogs - Flashback,President,0,0,0,,this doesn't even count as violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.30,0:11:27.54,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,この程度　暴力の内にも入らん
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.95,0:11:38.76,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,速度が落ちて落下コースに入ったか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.08,0:11:38.76,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,We're slowing down, preparing for descent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.76,0:11:41.70,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,We have just over ten minutes until impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.96,0:11:41.72,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,激突まであと十数分だな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.24,0:11:45.50,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.26,0:11:45.51,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,理解した
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.68,0:11:46.60,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,なに
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.84,0:11:46.58,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.19,0:11:50.84,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.26,0:11:50.85,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,待て
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.68,0:11:55.64,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,He ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.70,0:11:55.75,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,逃げた…だと
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.16,0:12:13.96,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,先刻　貴様を理解できぬと云った台詞　取り消そう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.16,0:12:14.38,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,I take back what I said about not \Nbeing able to understand you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.73,0:12:16.00,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,理解した
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.83,0:12:16.13,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,I understand you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.24,0:12:22.98,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,人虎　貴様はいつも誰かから生きる許可を貰う為に戦っている
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.34,0:12:23.05,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,Weretiger, you fight in order \Nto earn permission to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.72,0:12:26.63,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,Even if that means \Nsacrificing your own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.91,0:12:26.69,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,自らの命すら擲って
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.39,0:12:30.47,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,実に不快だ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.47,0:12:30.56,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,Disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.75,0:12:36.31,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,本気で思うのか　人虎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.77,0:12:38.90,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,Do you honestly believe, weretiger, that \Nsomeone is out there to grant you permission?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.69,0:12:38.90,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,許可を出す誰かがいると
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.67,0:12:41.94,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,他者の為　血を吐き戦えば
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.73,0:12:43.61,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,Did you think that if you put your \Nlife on the line fighting for others,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.35,0:12:46.41,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,誰かが生きる価値ありと書かれた判を押してくれると思ったか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.61,0:12:46.49,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,someone will stamp a form certifying \Nthat you deserve to live?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.07,0:12:49.62,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,Where's the crime in believing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.12,0:12:49.37,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,そう思うことの何が悪い
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.99,0:12:52.03,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,You're an utter disappointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.00,0:12:52.04,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,とんだ期待外れだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.26,0:12:55.09,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,貴様がこれほどまでに愚かとは
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.36,0:12:55.25,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,I never expected you to be such a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.09,0:12:59.67,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,これでは　仮令貴様を百回殺そうと　何の戦果にもならん
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.25,0:12:59.67,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,I could kill you hundreds of times, and I'd \Nhave gained no accomplishments in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.12,0:13:02.59,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,戦果だと？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.26,0:13:02.72,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,Accomplishments in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.59,0:13:03.68,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,然り
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.72,0:13:03.67,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.10,0:13:06.32,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,それが唯一絶対の価値
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.22,0:13:06.59,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,That is the only true measure of value.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.59,0:13:10.60,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,Without any accomplishments in battle, \Nthat man would never approve of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.74,0:13:10.60,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,戦果無き限り　あの人は僕を認めぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.02,0:13:14.06,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,Not Dazai-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.03,0:13:13.74,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,太宰さんは決して…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.32,0:13:16.77,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,太宰さん？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.39,0:13:16.77,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,Dazai-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.24,0:13:20.11,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,How does his name fit here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.30,0:13:19.99,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,何故そこで太宰さんの名前が出るんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.42,0:13:28.60,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,見つけたぞ　ストレイドッグス
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.45,0:13:28.66,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,I've found you, stray dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.72,0:13:34.54,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,Kyouka-chan, everyone has \Nstrengths and weaknesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.73,0:13:32.04,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,鏡花ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.34,0:13:34.54,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,人には向き不向きがある
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.89,0:13:37.92,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,そして君には明らかな殺しの才能がある
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.96,0:13:38.00,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,You clearly have talent in killing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.49,0:13:43.05,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,だから君は探偵社員にはなれない　君はそう思ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.55,0:13:43.05,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,You think that, therefore, you can't \Nbecome a member of the Detective Agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.42,0:13:45.22,Stray Dogs - Italics,Dazai,0,0,0,,That's foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.50,0:13:45.16,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,まったく莫迦莫迦しい
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.59,0:13:50.24,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,その考えが如何に根拠薄弱か　一秒で証明して見せよう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.63,0:13:50.35,Stray Dogs - Italics,Dazai,0,0,0,,I'll prove to you in one second how \Ndevoid of reason that belief is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.17,0:13:54.74,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,鏡花ちゃん　君はその手で何人殺した
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.22,0:13:54.89,Stray Dogs - Italics,Dazai,0,0,0,,Kyouka-chan, how many people have \Nyou killed with those hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.91,0:13:57.37,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,三十五人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.98,0:13:57.44,Stray Dogs - Default,Kyouka,0,0,0,,35.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.90,0:14:00.02,Stray Dogs - Italics,Dazai,0,0,0,,A mere 35.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.06,0:14:00.02,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,高が三十五人くらいなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.77,0:14:04.28,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,いいかい　鏡花ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.94,0:14:04.36,Stray Dogs - Italics,Dazai,0,0,0,,Listen up, Kyouka-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.29,0:14:07.95,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,You don't know everything \Nabout the Detective Agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.36,0:14:07.82,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,君は探偵社の凡てを知らない
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.47,0:14:10.87,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,You don't know everything about yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.49,0:14:10.96,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,自分自身の凡ても知らない
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.56,0:14:14.20,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,凡てを知ることは誰にもできない
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.66,0:14:14.20,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,No one can know everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.62,0:14:17.16,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,That's what we call "potential."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.63,0:14:17.05,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,それを「可能性」というんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.29,0:14:20.79,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,Even Atsushi-kun, who's \Ngiven you another chance,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.31,0:14:23.17,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,君に契機をくれた敦君だって　元は災害指定猛獣だ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.79,0:14:23.17,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,was originally a savage \Nbeast, deemed a menace.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.87,0:14:30.51,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,But now he's risking his own life to do what \Nonly he can do, in order to protect this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.89,0:14:28.25,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,でも今　彼は彼にしかできないことを命懸けでやってる
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.80,0:14:31.01,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,この街を守る為にね
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.51,0:14:37.52,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.73,0:14:38.98,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,あれだ　貨物用昇降機
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.52,0:14:38.98,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,The cargo elevator.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.90,0:14:50.72,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,あんな桁外れの異能力に勝てるわけない
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.95,0:14:49.70,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,His ability is way out of my league.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.70,0:14:50.86,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,I don't stand a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.27,0:14:54.37,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,隙を見て端末を奪う方法を考えないと
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.37,0:14:54.49,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,I need to think of a way to steal \Nthe terminal when I have a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.90,0:14:58.16,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,You're as foolish as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.91,0:14:58.16,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,相変わらず愚かな奴だ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.16,0:14:59.19,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,なに
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.16,0:14:59.46,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.46,0:15:03.54,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,This box takes us to the \Ninescapable deck service door.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.57,0:15:03.62,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,この箱の行き先は　逃げ場無き甲板搬入口
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.03,0:15:07.42,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,袋小路に追い込まれたのは僕らのほうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.05,0:15:07.59,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,We are the ones who have been cornered.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.10,0:15:09.17,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.17,0:15:09.34,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.58,0:15:15.35,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,この程度の輩に一度は敗れたとは　屈辱の極みだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.58,0:15:15.68,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,Nothing could be more shameful than to have \Nbeen defeated once by the likes of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.59,0:15:20.08,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,しかも生きてよい理由を他者に求めるようなくだらぬ輩に
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.68,0:15:20.27,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,Especially knowing that you're so worthless \Nthat you ask others for your own right to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.27,0:15:22.23,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,You're right, I'm worthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.39,0:15:22.41,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,確かに僕はくだらない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.90,0:15:27.95,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,でもお前みたいに　力を誇示したいだけの殺人鬼より百倍はマシだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.94,0:15:26.69,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,But you're a murderer with no purpose \Nbut to flaunt your strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.69,0:15:27.65,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,I'm a hundred times better.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.12,0:15:29.40,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,Say that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.19,0:15:29.37,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,なんだと
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.37,0:15:31.66,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,力も地位も十分あるのに
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.40,0:15:31.66,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,You have plenty of power and status.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.07,0:15:34.66,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ただみんなに怖がられたいから戦うなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.16,0:15:34.66,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,You fight just so that people fear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.66,0:15:36.71,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,That's way more worthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.87,0:15:36.94,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,そのほうがよほどくだらな…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.78,0:15:40.25,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,Take that back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.79,0:15:40.04,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,取り消せ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.83,0:15:44.89,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,僕に力も地位もあるだと？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.87,0:15:45.00,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,I have power and status?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.78,0:15:50.88,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,貴様を不快だと云った理由を教えてやる
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.84,0:15:50.67,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,I'll tell you why I called you disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.14,0:15:53.97,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,それは貴様が　凡てを持っていながら
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.16,0:15:59.14,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,It's because you're a fool who continues to \Nmope about old wounds despite having everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.97,0:15:58.90,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,そのことに気付きもせず　己が古傷に甘え続ける愚か者だからだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.76,0:16:02.77,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,なに　僕がなんだって
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.81,0:16:00.73,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.23,0:16:02.77,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,What did you say I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.77,0:16:04.61,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,You're blessed with your gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.77,0:16:05.99,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,異能力に恵まれ　出逢いに恵まれ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.61,0:16:06.23,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,You're blessed with friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.23,0:16:10.11,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,With no effort and with nothing but sheer \Nluck, you're revered and praised by Dazai-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.33,0:16:10.02,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,努力もぜず　ただ運だけで太宰さんに認め讃えられながら
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.02,0:16:14.24,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,貴様はその幸福にも気付かず　己の悲劇ばかりに浸る
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.11,0:16:12.77,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,You don't even understand how lucky you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.77,0:16:14.24,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,You dwell in your own tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.24,0:16:15.58,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,You're a disgusting fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.24,0:16:15.58,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,愚物だからだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.95,0:16:21.94,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,Without any accomplishments in battle, \Nthat man would never approve of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.99,0:16:21.96,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,戦果なき限り　あの人は僕を認めぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.38,0:16:25.42,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,Not Dazai-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.38,0:16:25.42,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,太宰さんは決して…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.28,0:16:28.92,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,太宰さんって
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.29,0:16:28.92,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,Dazai-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.65,0:16:32.63,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,まさかお前　ずっと…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.67,0:16:32.55,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you've always been...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.94,0:16:47.94,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,鬼遊はそろそろ終わりにしよう
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.15,0:16:48.19,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,That's enough of playing tag.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.19,0:16:53.07,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,In less than ten minutes, the Moby Dick \Nwill enter into an irrevocable trajectory.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.21,0:16:52.64,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,あと十分足らずで「白鯨」の高度は復行限界を下回る
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.07,0:16:58.70,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,At that point, not even this terminal will \Nbe able to stop it from falling into the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.13,0:16:54.63,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,それを過ぎれば
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.09,0:16:58.47,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,この端末でも街への落下を防げない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.70,0:17:03.79,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,Only I will survive, as I've \Nstrengthened myself with my ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.93,0:17:03.64,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,生き残るのは　異能力で身体強化した俺だけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.79,0:17:10.72,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,Hey, nouveau riche, if I defeat someone as \Nstrong as you, will I no longer be weak?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.85,0:17:05.49,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,成金背広
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.04,0:17:10.58,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,貴様ほどの強者を倒せば　僕も弱者ではなくなるか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.10,0:17:15.67,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,I'll guarantee it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.15,0:17:15.68,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,保証しよう
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.67,0:17:19.51,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,Then I won't regret dying \Nas many times as it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.68,0:17:19.45,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ならばこの身がいくつ砕けようとも　惜しくはない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.54,0:17:21.85,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,「羅生門」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.60,0:17:30.02,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,Rashoumon! Demonic Armor!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.04,0:17:26.11,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,天魔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.74,0:17:29.99,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,纏鎧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.20,0:17:49.16,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,異能力で体を強制操作しているのか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.29,0:17:49.12,Stray Dogs - Italics,Francis,0,0,0,,Is he overriding my actions with his gift?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.83,0:17:59.10,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,芥川はあんなに強いのに　自分のことを弱者だと思ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.92,0:17:59.09,Stray Dogs - Italics,Atsushi,0,0,0,,Akutagawa is so strong, yet \Nhe thinks of himself as weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.55,0:18:01.64,Stray Dogs - Italics,Atsushi,0,0,0,,He's preposterous!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.68,0:18:01.70,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,だとしたら言語道断だ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.97,0:18:04.81,Stray Dogs - Italics,Atsushi,0,0,0,,How many people has his selfishness killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.18,0:18:04.94,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,その身勝手で何人死んだと思ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.85,0:18:11.40,Stray Dogs - Italics,Atsushi,0,0,0,,Tiger, grant me strength once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.06,0:18:08.05,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,虎よ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.29,0:18:11.34,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,もう一度僕に力を…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.90,0:18:13.53,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,あの時のように
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.90,0:18:13.82,Stray Dogs - Italics,Atsushi,0,0,0,,Just like last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.92,0:18:27.79,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,Get out of my way, weretiger!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.07,0:18:27.47,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,邪魔するな　人虎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.47,0:18:29.34,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,お前こそ　邪魔をするな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.79,0:18:29.75,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,{\i1}You{\i0} get out of {\i1}my{\i0} way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.96,0:18:32.93,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,Dazai-san, my ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.97,0:18:32.92,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,何が太宰さんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.92,0:18:34.72,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,お前のほうがくだらない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.93,0:18:34.63,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,You're even more worthless!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.63,0:18:35.67,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,Nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.72,0:18:37.70,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,笑止　僕より貴様のほうがくだらぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.67,0:18:37.80,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,You're more worthless than I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.70,0:18:38.94,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,面白い
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.80,0:18:39.09,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,This is amusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.14,0:18:43.68,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,You're both very much alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.26,0:18:43.77,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,君達は　実に似た者同士だ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.21,0:18:45.93,Stray Dogs - Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.34,0:18:45.93,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,なに
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.22,0:18:47.64,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,こんな奴と
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.26,0:18:47.64,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi; Akutagawa,0,0,0,,Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.64,0:18:49.26,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi; Akutagawa,0,0,0,,...compare me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.64,0:18:49.27,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,一緒に
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.26,0:18:51.77,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi; Akutagawa,0,0,0,,...to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.27,0:18:51.77,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,するな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.83,0:19:08.36,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,黒布に鎧と外筋の役を担わせるこの技
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.90,0:19:08.66,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,This technique makes my black \Narmor double as muscle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.05,0:19:11.11,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,My body is too feeble to last.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.09,0:19:11.13,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,脆弱な肉体が持たぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.35,0:19:14.04,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,休憩か　芥川
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.50,0:19:14.04,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,Taking a break, Akutagawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.04,0:19:14.79,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.04,0:19:16.01,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,黙れ　次は貴様だ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.79,0:19:16.01,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,You're next.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.18,0:19:18.33,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,制御端末が先だ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.34,0:19:18.56,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,The control terminal comes first.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.56,0:19:22.65,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,If this ship hits the city, \NDazai-san will be obliterated, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.71,0:19:22.64,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,この船が街に落ちたら　太宰さんまで吹き飛ぶだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.53,0:19:26.35,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,あの人がこの程度で死ぬものか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.55,0:19:26.35,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,That man wouldn't die so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.08,0:19:34.95,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,道標　教えてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.15,0:19:37.07,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,Tiger beetle, tell me, is \Nthere anything in this world
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.49,0:19:40.08,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,この世界で凡てを犠牲にする価値のあるものが
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.07,0:19:42.90,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,aside from family worth \Nsacrificing everything for?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.08,0:19:42.91,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,家族以外に存在すると思うか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.51,0:19:49.23,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,I'll take the book, and I'll bring \Nmy daughter back into this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.58,0:19:45.72,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は「本」を手に入れる
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.05,0:19:49.19,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,そして娘をこの世に呼び戻す
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.19,0:19:50.22,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,娘？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.23,0:19:50.16,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,Your daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.64,0:20:03.26,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,My wife, Zelda, unable to accept our \Ndaughter's death, became mentally ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.92,0:20:03.33,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,妻ゼルダは　娘の死を受け止められず　心を病み
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.26,0:20:08.62,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,To this day, she hides in her fantasy that \Nour daughter is studying abroad in London.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.33,0:20:08.62,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,娘はロンドンに留学中という妄想の中に　今も逃げ込んでいる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.32,0:20:13.69,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,俺はその妄想を現実にし　家族を取り戻す
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.43,0:20:13.81,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,I'm going to make that fantasy a reality,\N and reclaim my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.57,0:20:16.86,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,No matter what the cost is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.57,0:20:16.86,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,どんな犠牲を払っても
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.28,0:20:20.48,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,My wealth is dispensable.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.35,0:20:20.58,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,処分可能な俺の資産
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.09,0:20:27.35,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,その凡てを支払う
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.16,0:20:27.41,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,I'll pay all of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.61,0:20:37.30,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,桁違いだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.67,0:20:37.29,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,He's off the scales.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.71,0:20:41.04,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,It's like standing in front \Nof a massive tornado.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.87,0:20:40.73,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,まるで巨大の竜巻の前にいるみたいな…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.82,0:20:45.49,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,これが　ギルドの長の覚悟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.92,0:20:45.59,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,This is the will of the Guild's leader?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.92,0:21:06.90,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,Akutagawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.92,0:21:06.91,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,芥川
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.90,0:21:08.13,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.03,0:21:08.12,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.82,0:21:12.46,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,僕は　愚かか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.91,0:21:12.82,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,Am I a fool?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.33,0:21:16.52,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,あの記憶から逃げたいと思うことはくだらないか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.46,0:21:16.67,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,Is it worthless of me to want \Nto escape from those memories?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.11,0:21:19.29,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ　くだらぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.13,0:21:19.59,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.92,0:21:25.79,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,The words of your past are fundamentally \Nunrelated to who you are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.92,0:21:25.80,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,何故なら　苦しめる過去の言葉と貴様は　本質的に無関係だからだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.34,0:21:33.27,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,そうか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.56,0:21:33.56,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.13,0:21:40.01,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,太宰さんは　とっくにお前を認めてると思うぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.23,0:21:39.73,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,I think Dazai-san already approved \Nof you a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.61,0:21:49.64,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,来い
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.78,0:21:49.74,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0,0,0,,Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.89,0:21:53.65,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,「月下獣・半人半虎」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.91,0:21:53.57,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0,0,0,,Beast Beneath the Moonlight!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.82,0:21:58.65,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,「羅生門・天魔纏鎧」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.83,0:21:58.54,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0,0,0,,Rashoumon Demonic Armor!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.07,0:21:58.53,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,君の苦悩は君だけのものじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.22,0:22:01.86,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,成りたいものと向いてるものが違う時
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.06,0:22:03.56,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,人はどうすればいい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.46,0:22:08.16,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,生き方の正解を知りたくて　誰もが戦ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.01,0:22:10.01,sign_35508_287_Episode_24,Text,0,0,0,,Episode 24
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.01,0:22:10.01,sign_35508_288_If_I_May_Shed_Aw,Text,0,0,0,,If I May Shed Away \NMy Burden Now
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.74,0:22:10.52,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,何を求め戦う
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.73,0:22:12.11,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,どうやって生きる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.52,0:22:14.63,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,答えは誰も教えてくれない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.91,0:22:18.66,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,我々にあるのはただ迷う権利だけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.55,0:22:22.01,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,次回　第二十四話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.35,0:22:25.24,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,若し今日この荷物を降ろして善いのなら
